{"tid":652192,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"雖然唔妥香港人，但可唔可以唔好咁明顯？","createTime":"2018-05-03T16:08:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T16:58:18.000Z","uid":104965,"like":53,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a3b15015fcc0edcab7aba30343370f649bb3a7bf","tid":652192,"uid":104965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T16:08:20.000Z","msg":"高樓價 - 讓香港人唔敢結婚生仔<br />\n封殺廣東話 - 係母語都唔准人認？<br />\n相信只是港府傭人自作聰明，英明的中央人民政府懲罰港府吧！<br />\n<br />\n其實香港人好簡單<br />\n安居樂業，有餘錢的話可以旅行玩玩已經感恩不盡<br />\n<br />\n為何偉大的中央人民政府要由得特區無能政府亂搞？<br />\n<br />\n以前英治時期無真民主，其實現在都唔需要太大改變。<br />\n但係廣大香港人的民生生活質素一定要進步！最少要保持到質素，住得有尊嚴！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果搞到民生問題，香港一定亂。<br />\n中央說：香港不能亂。<br />\n<br />\n那請先撤走無能的傭人，讓有能者登上代理人一職。<br />\n<br />\n請求：讓庸碌無能的教育局長退下來吧。他做事說話太愚鈍及欠說服力，以致在母語事件惹人發笑，嚴重影響中央人民政府在香港的形象。"},{"pid":"9f4b1030bf204cf255b86ce423e9ae1e7f453a39","tid":652192,"uid":99205,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T16:22:14.000Z","msg":"不能亂?<img src=\"https://gss1.bdstatic.com/9vo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/w%3D268%3Bg%3D0/sign=11797e98e324b899de3c7e3e563d7aa8/0823dd54564e9258e848d2769682d158ccbf4e2d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgss1.bdstatic.com%2F9vo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy%2Fbaike%2Fw%253D268%253Bg%253D0%2Fsign%3D11797e98e324b899de3c7e3e563d7aa8%2F0823dd54564e9258e848d2769682d158ccbf4e2d.jpg&h=18c5cace&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n愈亂愈好<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://resize2-parismatch.ladmedia.fr/r/625,417,center-middle,ffffff/img/var/news/storage/images/paris-match/vivre/luxe/le-design-s-eveille-a-pekin-159299/1647492-1-fre-FR/Le-design-s-eveille-a-Pekin.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fresize2-parismatch.ladmedia.fr%2Fr%2F625%2C417%2Ccenter-middle%2Cffffff%2Fimg%2Fvar%2Fnews%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Fparis-match%2Fvivre%2Fluxe%2Fle-design-s-eveille-a-pekin-159299%2F1647492-1-fre-FR%2FLe-design-s-eveille-a-Pekin.jpg&h=9a28b45f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"46121030c8c6a198cec907